{"tid":1378911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知點解每次罷工都收皮","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:40:36.000Z","uid":43978,"like":112,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"69126315734b202193fe0f6558d1af75c6d7c6e4","tid":1378911,"uid":43978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:00:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為每次都係前一日先決定唔夠民宣</span></span><br />\n所以我地而家開始推8月五號三罷<br />\n等大家夠時間醞釀 處理<br />\n亦希望今個星期唔好有任何有關返工嘅不合作運動<br />\n下星期一鋪過爆鳩政府<br />\n最最最希望 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">公務員 港鐵車長 九巴車長</span> 參與 一齊真正令全城癱瘓<br />\n<br />\n我係度呼籲黎緊8月5號(星期一)香港全民大罷工逼使政府回應五大訢求!<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n一個都不能少 <br />\n不流血，不受傷，不被捕<br />\n不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8979d00b19d17737796b5e69b9d06ccad2f74714","tid":1378911,"uid":43978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:00:59.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"1ef3f685395ef601d7d77019861b9f1cb9168578","tid":1378911,"uid":90328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:01:26.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"0f55612c5d5dc19fe07c3c16965157722563aa60","tid":1378911,"uid":43978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:01:40.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"d6dff9bfdda76e659c2fc446bcd9e2395c71af73","tid":1378911,"uid":43978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:01:53.000Z","msg":"一齊罷工"},{"pid":"5ecbe10af847d386a322601ec0f31c8f3fcde33d","tid":1378911,"uid":43978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:02:30.000Z","msg":"真正三罷 比壓力"},{"pid":"755449f083040d2ba274b6e4f587198c0d7a08e3","tid":1378911,"uid":131884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"7de3fce12a03dcfb4738628377879cc5c313c669","tid":1378911,"uid":3427,"like":0,"dislike":