slike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:10:39.000Z","msg":"30吧車長罷工 最容易令大家配合罷工喎"},{"pid":"45d0affa204958c4db543f7a0ac5f9a30dfb9e66","tid":1378911,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:10:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家好尊重合約精神。<br />\n到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！"},{"pid":"8e7d6bb1be6e119865443254e6b449a9875d75f0","tid":1378911,"uid":43978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9891cf0750ccbaed7532020a1e1d4ebf8ce70580","tid":1378911,"uid":66346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:10:39.000Z","msg":"30吧車長罷工 最容易令大家配合罷工喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"30 車長會罷？"},{"pid":"587e71c0a0897f8f44a32bb12a1bd57f1442bf41","tid":1378911,"uid":11436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:15:08.000Z","msg":"一定罷！"},{"pid":"f7eae8521dafb3ee81f851849c84870ccf921948","tid":1378911,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:16:45.000Z","msg":"呢d要入tg